      <title>旧机荣耀9折腾之termux实现archLinux</title>
      <link href="/2023/05/27/%E6%97%A7%E6%9C%BA%E8%8D%A3%E8%80%809%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE%E4%B9%8Btermux%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0archLinux/"/>
      <url>/2023/05/27/%E6%97%A7%E6%9C%BA%E8%8D%A3%E8%80%809%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE%E4%B9%8Btermux%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0archLinux/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="旧机荣耀9折腾之termux实现archLinux"><a href="#旧机荣耀9折腾之termux实现archLinux" class="headerlink" title="旧机荣耀9折腾之termux实现archLinux"></a>旧机荣耀9折腾之termux实现archLinux</h1><h2 id="电脑ssh登录手机termux（可选）"><a href="#电脑ssh登录手机termux（可选）" class="headerlink" title="电脑ssh登录手机termux（可选）"></a>电脑ssh登录手机termux（可选）</h2><p>安装openssh</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt update</span><br><span class="line">apt install openssh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动sshd服务</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sshd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置自动启动ssh服务</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">echo &quot;sshd&quot; &gt;&gt; ~/.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>手机查看当前用户名</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">whoami</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>手机查看当前ip</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ifconfig -a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/05/27/X4lrSU7zAjJwHTK.jpg" alt="Screenshot_20220421_134345.jpg" style="zoom:67%;" /><p>我的手机当前的ip为 ：192.168.43.131<br>修改ssh密码</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">passwd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>pc连接ssh</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -p 8022 u0_a100@192.168.43.131</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装ArchLinux"><a href="#安装ArchLinux" class="headerlink" title="安装ArchLinux"></a>安装ArchLinux</h1><p>Termux提供了一个proot-distro软件包，用于管理Termux内部的Linux发行版。据说几乎没有性能损失。</p><p>您可以通过执行以下命令安装该实用程序<br>安装proot-distro</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg install proot-distro</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 查询支持哪些发行版本</span><br><span class="line">proot-distro list1</span><br><span class="line">proot-distro install &lt;alias&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我安装的 是archlinux，如下命令：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">proot-distro install archlinux</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 进入archlinux</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">proot-distro login archlinux</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>执行结果如下：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~ $ proot-distro login archlinux</span><br><span class="line">[root@localhost ~]#</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="ArchLinux换源"><a href="#ArchLinux换源" class="headerlink" title="ArchLinux换源"></a>ArchLinux换源</h2><p>编辑 &#x2F;etc&#x2F;pacman.d&#x2F;mirrorlist ，在文件的顶端添加<code>Server = https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/archlinuxarm/$arch/$repo</code>：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="vim的简单使用："><a href="#vim的简单使用：" class="headerlink" title="vim的简单使用："></a>vim的简单使用：</h3><p>编辑“text.txt”:<code>vim text.txt</code>（打开文件并编辑，如果没有这个文件则创建）</p><p>插入模式:<code>i</code></p><p>向下搜索:<code>/</code></p><p>向上搜索:<code>?</code></p><p>退出插入模式:<code>esc</code></p><p>保存:<code>:w</code></p><p>退出:<code>:q</code></p><p>不保存退出:<code>:q!</code></p><p>保存退出:<code>:wq!</code>（也可以是:qw  :qw!  :wq ）（大雾）<br>我的编辑：</p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/05/27/uwsAxt8YCEeaJhP.jpg" alt="Screenshot_20220421_135802_com.termux.jpg" style="zoom:67%;" /><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/05/27/CONbJtspjPUS9Mm.jpg" alt="Screenshot_20220421_140005_com.termux.jpg" style="zoom:67%;" /><p>使用pacman安装软件之前先更新一下系统：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#更新系统，不然可能安装软件报错</span><br><span class="line">pacman -Syyu</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>archlinux安装软件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#安装vim</span><br><span class="line">pacman -S vim</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>neofetch</code></p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/05/27/TDof8HgRQzUtFIq.jpg" alt="Screenshot_20220421_144813_com.termux.jpg" style="zoom:67%;" /><h2 id="安装设置中文"><a href="#安装设置中文" class="headerlink" title="安装设置中文"></a>安装设置中文</h2><p>查看当前语言环境:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">echo $LANG</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看当前系统是否有中文语言包</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">locale -a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果没有中文语言包</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/locale.gen</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看文件中是否有zh_CN.UTF-8，如果没有在文件中增加一行</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">zh_CN.UTF-8 UTF-8</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>略<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/lxyoucan/article/details/116743502">https://blog.csdn.net/lxyoucan/article/details/116743502</a></p><h2 id="安装Xwindow"><a href="#安装Xwindow" class="headerlink" title="安装Xwindow"></a>安装Xwindow</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S xorg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下载93.06mib（20220421）</p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/05/27/jQGFArh8KfVu7IL.jpg" alt="Screenshot_20220421_152142_com.termux.jpg" style="zoom:67%;" />这近乎消失的网速。。。<p>安装桌面环境和相关软件(大量包，一路回车)</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S xfce4 xfce4-goodies</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下载102.75mib（而且好费时间）</p><p>安装字体</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S ttf-dejavu wqy-bitmapfont wqy-microhei wqy-zenhei noto-fonts noto-fonts-emoji</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>45.05mib</p><p>安装网络管理</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S networkmanager</span><br><span class="line">systemctl enable NetworkManager # 开机自启动</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="配置nvc"><a href="#配置nvc" class="headerlink" title="配置nvc"></a>配置nvc</h2><p>termux 安装 tigervnc</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt install x11-repo #安装X11源</span><br><span class="line">apt install tigervnc xorg-xhost</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置vnc启动脚本</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nano vnc</span><br><span class="line">写入如下内容</span><br><span class="line">vncserver -kill :1 #关掉上次未关的vnc,不写也可以！</span><br><span class="line">vncserver -geometry 1920x1080 -listen tcp :1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/05/27/7Eu5SFD2hbsZlzk.jpg" alt="Screenshot_20220421_161315.jpg" style="zoom:67%;" /><blockquote><p>nano基本使用：ctrl+o保存，ctrl+x退出</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nano host</span><br><span class="line">#写入以下内容</span><br><span class="line">DISPLAY=:1 xhost +</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nano startarchvnc# 编辑启动arch vnc的脚本</span><br><span class="line">#在这里写入</span><br><span class="line">sh vnc</span><br><span class="line">sh host</span><br><span class="line">proot-distro login archlinux</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输入<code>sh startarchvnc</code> 进入到arch系统中会让你设置vnc的密码，设置即可<br>我设置的是<code>20220421</code></p><p>进入arch系统输入<code>DISPLAY=:1 xfce4-session</code></p><p>打开VNC Viewer软件，接入本地链接：</p><blockquote><p>localhost:1<br>arch</p></blockquote><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/05/27/ZdHn9wIotbV4QRX.jpg" alt="Screenshot_20220421_183303_com.realvnc.viewer.android.jpg" style="zoom:67%;" />开启xfce桌面！！！<p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/05/27/DnAMQkvC7aNH2i5.jpg" alt="Screenshot_20220421_164353_com.realvnc.viewer.android.jpg"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
